# rs_audio_stats

ğŸµ Professional-grade audio analysis and normalization library for Python with EBU R128 loudness measurement.

[![PyPI version](https://badge.fury.io/py/rs-audio-stats.svg)](https://pypi.org/project/rs-audio-stats/)
